---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About | Hyrox Guide"
  description="About HyroxGuide — who we are, our mission, and why we built the most comprehensive Hyrox resource online."
>
  <section class="container-main py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-8">
        <span class="text-gradient-accent">About HyroxGuide</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-xl text-text-muted leading-relaxed">
          HyroxGuide is the most comprehensive free resource for everything Hyrox —
          race guides, training programs, gear reviews, and competition calendars.
        </p>

        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          We believe everyone deserves access to high-quality training information.
          Hyrox is the fastest-growing fitness competition in the world, and whether
          you're training for your first race or chasing a podium finish, we want to
          help you perform your best.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Cover</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Racing Guide:</strong> Complete breakdown of the Hyrox format, every station, every category</li>
          <li><strong>Training Programs:</strong> Structured plans from beginner to advanced, plus station-specific drills</li>
          <li><strong>Gear Reviews:</strong> Honest recommendations for shoes, clothing, and equipment</li>
          <li><strong>Competition Calendar:</strong> Up-to-date listing of upcoming Hyrox races worldwide</li>
          <li><strong>Blog:</strong> Race recaps, training tips, and community stories</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <p>
          Some links on this site are affiliate links. When you purchase through these
          links, we may earn a small commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us
          keep the site running and free for everyone. We only recommend products we've
          tested or genuinely believe will help your Hyrox performance.
        </p>

        <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
        <p>
          HyroxGuide is an independent resource and is not affiliated with, endorsed by,
          or officially connected to Hyrox GmbH. All trademarks and brand names mentioned
          on this site belong to their respective owners.
        </p>

        <h2>Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Got a question, suggestion, or want to collaborate? Reach out to us at
          <a href="mailto:hello@hyroxguide.com">hello@hyroxguide.com</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
